text: It's time to build a moth trap! Here is how you get started:
Here are the rest of the Instructions for Building a Moth Trap!

Moth Traps

What do you think a moth trap should look like?

Think-Pair-Share

  • Sketch and label your own idea
  • Note attributes of a good trap in a Sketch Tile or Text Tile and share with your group and class.

Build Traps

Look closely at your teacher's trap

Compare/Contrast How does yours look like your teacher's? What is different?

Discuss possible trap locations and make notes by using a Text Tile

Classroom Management

Have activities going on like moth games, or watching a moth life cycle video while the other groups are waiting to build with their teacher
